text: Ibnu Saleh (8 October 1961 - 4 October 2020) was an Indonesian politician. He was born in Prabumulih, Indonesia. He was a member of the Nasdem Party. Between 2016 to 2017, he was Deputy Regent of the Central Bangka Regency. In 2017, he became the Regent. Saleh died on 4 October 2020 at a hospital in Pangkal Pinang, Indonesia from COVID-19, four days before his 59th birthday.Positif COVID-19, Bupati Bangka Tengah Meninggal Dunia ==References== Category:1961 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Deaths from the COVID-19 pandemic in Indonesia Category:Indonesian politicians
